title: Ep. 75 "The Lifestyle" ft. JD & Ingrid
description:
JD & Ingrid join us this week. They quickly school us on the fact they're not swingers, they are in "the lifestyle". They break down how they became a part of it, who gets to join, their type, rejection, and so much more!
